---
title: Kids' Veggie Pita Pizzas Serves 2 | with Crunchy Carrot Stick Dippers
description: Make lunchtime decisions easy with these quick veggie pitas! Topped with mozzarella and fresh bell peppers, these fun and kid-friendly 'pizzas' will have your littles running for seconds.
